ChartQuery serverCacheWarehouse1 - The chart request data to Whaly query server2 - We check if there is data in cache for this query (from a previous load) - if yes we check if the cache is stale by using the cache strategy configuration - if the cache is stale, we query the warehouse to get fresh data for the chart - if the cache is still valid, we use with the cached value3 - If needed, we query the Warehouse to get fresh data for the chartsWe periodically query the Warehouse to check if the base data in the Warehouse has changed.
